      • AttributeType

        protected AttributeType(long _id,
             String _uuid,
             String _name,
             String _dbAttrTypeName,
             String _uiAttrTypeName)
                 throws EFapsException
        This is the constructor for class Attribute. Every instance of class Attribute must have a name (parameter _name) and an identifier (parameter _id).
        Parameters:
        _id - id of the attribute
        _uuid - universal unique identifier
        _name - name of the instance
        _dbAttrTypeName - name of the database attribute type
        _uiAttrTypeName - name of the user interface attribute type
        Throws:
        EFapsException - if attribute type for the data model or user interface could not be initialized
